title: NFL Around the League: AFC East Preview- August 14th, 2013
itunes:title: NFL Around the League: AFC East Preview- August 14th, 2013
description:
Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling go over Tom Brady's injury scare, Hard Knocks, and the rest of the headlines you should know. We also start our division-by-division season previews with the AFC East. Projected records and standings for all! Join the conversation and tweet us @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.
